ALCON:  Tomorrow night=E2=80=99s (Thursday) videoconference is =
preparation for the TNMAN Final Planning Meeting (FPM) to be held at =
Sidco on 26/27MAR2026.=20

TNSG is assigned the two locations discussed below by National Guard=E2=80=
=99s Lt Sussman: Holston for 3rd (engineering - LIDAR assessment and =
SECFOR) and Caney Fork Welcome Center (engineering - bridge assessment =
and SECFOR). See LT Sussman=E2=80=99s email to TNSG with his questions =
for us, and which will serve as our Agenda for tomorrow night.

We have many of the answers of the questions below, and we need to =
answer the following questions:
Specific missions for each site
Finalize engineering assignments: LIDAR mapping and SECFOR at Holston; =
bridge assessment and drone activity at Caney Fork
Transportation of engineers to Holston if we accept that mission
Date(s) of participation

Videoconference for our meeting tomorrow night is copied below for your =
convenience.

Attached is the TNMAN LOI from National Guard.

=EF=BF=BC

TNSG / TNMAN Final Planning Meeting Preparation Videoconference
Thursday, March 19 =C2=B7  (1800-1900CT) ) (1900-2000 ET)
